+				 * | /  _----> Headphone (HP) Right channel sink
+				 * | | /  _--> Internal Speaker (SP) sink
+				 * | | | /
+				 * | | | |     L/R - Left/Right channel source
+				 * 0 L-R X       X - Unrouted (muted) channel source
